Sakura Bloom Q + A 🌿 Q. I’m pregnant - can I still wear my little one throughout my pregnancy? If so, what Sakura Bloom is the best for babywearing while pregnant?
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
A. Yes! All 3 of our carriers are specifically designed for comfortably wearing your toddler throughout your pregnancy. ❤️ Which one is “best” really comes down to your own personal preference + aesthetics - ask any member of our community and they will each have their own personal favorite. Here’s a little bit about how each carrier functions in pregnancy... ⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⭐️ Our Onbuhimo is a waistless carrier that allows baby to sit high on your front or back making babywearing a breeze with nothing around your waist while keeping baby in the action being able to see over your shoulder. ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⭐️ Our Scout’s wide unpadded waist band actually supports your bump! Wear it under your bump to create added support through those heavy last few months, or wear it over your bump for a higher back carry similar to the Onbuhimo. It also has the added bonus of being able to carry either your newborn or your toddler once baby arrives!⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
